script.name: plugin.shiprename.renameobj
script.description: Ship Renaming: Rename the ship based on epressions
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.cycrow.shiprename' $name = $a.name
$name.array = array alloc: size=0 $current.colour = null
$colours = table alloc $colours['red'] = 10 $colours['blue'] = 11 $colours['green'] = 12 $colours['yellow'] = 13 $colours['cyan'] = 14 $colours['magenta'] = 15 $colours['grey'] = 16 $colours['gray'] = 16 $colours['white'] = 17
$cmds = table alloc $cmds[COMMAND_AUTOTRADER_SECTOR] = 102 $cmds[COMMAND_AUTOTRADER_UNIVERSE] = 100
while [TRUE] gosub sub.NextBracket
if not $str.code break else $str.replace = null if $str.code == 'maker' $maker = $a.obj ->get true maker race $str.replace = sprintf: fmt='%s', $maker, null, null, null, null else if $colours[$str.code] gosub sub.DoColour $current.colour = $str.code $str.before = null else if $str.code == 'normal' gosub sub.DoColour $current.colour = null $str.before = null else if $str.code == 'type' $page = $a.obj ->get object voice page $id = $a.obj ->get object voice id $str.replace = read text: page=$page id=$id else if $str.code == 'fulltype' $ware.code = $a.obj -> get ware type code of object $str.replace = sprintf: fmt='%s', $ware.code, null, null, null, null else if $str.code == 'variant' if $a.obj -> is of class Ship $vari = $a.obj -> get ship variation if $vari != [Vari.Basic] $id = 10000 + $vari $str.replace = read text: page=[Page.ObjDesc] id=$id end end else if $str.code == 'company' $str.replace = $a.company else if $str.code == 'initials' $str.replace = $a.companyi else if $str.code == 'shipid' do if $a.shipid $str.replace = sprintf: fmt='%s', $a.shipid, null, null, null, null else if $str.code == 'stationid' do if $a.stationid $str.replace = sprintf: fmt='%s', $a.stationid, null, null, null, null else if $str.code == 'sector' $str.replace = $a.obj -> get sector else if $str.code == 'cargo' if $a.obj -> is of class Ship $ship.cargo = $a.obj -> get cargo bay size $ship.cargo.used = $a.obj -> get total volume in cargo bay $percent = fixed multiply and divide: $ship.cargo.used * 100 / $ship.cargo $str.replace = sprintf: fmt='%s%%', $percent, null, null, null, null end else if $str.code == 'class' $ware.code = $a.obj -> get ware type code of object $str.replace = get class code from type: type=$ware.code else if $str.code == 'tradeskill' if $a.obj -> is of class Ship $speaker = $a.obj ->get pilot speaker if $speaker -> exists $skill = $speaker -> get pilot tradeskill $str.replace = sprintf: fmt='%s', $skill, null, null, null, null end end else if $str.code == 'homebase' if $a.obj -> is of class Ship $homebase = $a.obj -> get homebase do if $homebase -> exists $str.replace = $homebase -> get name end else if $str.code == 'cmd' if $a.obj -> is of class Ship if $a.obj ->is being managed $homebase = $a.obj -> get homebase if $homebase -> exists if $homebase -> is of class Station if $homebase -> is script plugin.stationmgr.run on stack of task=[Task.StationMgr] $str.replace = read text: page=$page.id id=103 end end end end if not $str.replace $ship.cmd = $a.obj -> get command if $ship.cmd == COMMAND_AUTOTRADER_SECTOR $cmd.target2 = $a.obj -> get command target2 do if $cmd.target2 >= 1 $str.replace = read text: page=$page.id id=101 end if not $str.replace $text.id = $cmds[$ship.cmd] do if $text.id $str.replace = read text: page=$page.id id=$text.id end end end
else if $str.code == 'short' do if $a.short $str.replace = $a.short
else if $str.code == 'cmd.short' if $a.obj -> is of class Ship $ship.cmd = $a.obj -> get command $str.replace = get command short name: command=$ship.cmd end
else if $str.code == 'flags' $str.replace = null if $a.obj -> is of class Ship if $a.obj ->is being managed $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104300 gosub sub.AddToReplace end if $a.obj -> is player wingman $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=4268 gosub sub.AddToReplace end if $a.obj -> is of class M7D $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104302 gosub sub.AddToReplace else if $a.obj -> is of class Carrier $managed.ships = $a.obj ->get managed ships if $managed.ships if size of array $managed.ships $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104301 gosub sub.AddToReplace end end end end end
if $str.replace do if $str.extra $str.replace = $str.extra + $str.replace if $str.before $name = $str.before + $str.replace + $str.after else $name = $str.replace + $str.after end else if $str.before $name = $str.before + $str.after else $name = $str.after end end end end
$str.before = $name gosub sub.DoColour do if size of array $name.array $name = combine string array: $name.array, separator=' ' return $name
sub.DoColour: if $str.before if get length of string $str.before if $current.colour $text.id = $colours[$current.colour] $read.text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=$text.id, $str.before, null, null, null, null append $read.text to array $name.array else append $str.before to array $name.array end end end $current.colour = null endsub
sub.NextBracket: $str.code = null if $name $pos = find position of pattern '[' in $name if $pos >= 0 $pos2 = find position of pattern ']' in $name if $pos2 <= $pos $str.begin = get substring of $name offset=0 length=$pos2 inc $pos2 = $str.end = get substring of $name offset=$pos2 length=null $name = $str.begin + $str.end else if $pos2 >= 0 $str.before = get substring of $name offset=0 length=$pos inc $pos = $len = $pos2 - $pos $str.code = get substring of $name offset=$pos length=$len inc $pos2 = $str.after = get substring of $name offset=$pos2 length=null else $str.begin = get substring of $name offset=0 length=$pos inc $pos = $str.end = get substring of $name offset=$pos length=null $name = $str.begin + $str.end end end
if $str.code $pos = find position of pattern '|' in $str.code if $pos >= 0 $pos2 = $pos + 1 $str.extra = get substring of $str.code offset=$pos2 length=null $str.code = get substring of $str.code offset=0 length=$pos end end end endsub
sub.AddToReplace: if $str.replace $str.replace = $str.replace + $read.text else $str.replace = $read.text end endsub return null
